        "bodyTextSample": "Library\nCapture\nAsk\nMore\nDevice pairing\n\nAI Memory is accessible at https://brain.arunp.in via the Cloudflare tunnel. Pair Android with a short-lived code, or use the advanced token flow for the Chrome extension.\n\nTHIS DEVICE\n\nAlready paired through your unlocked browser session.\n\nADD ANDROID DEVICE\nAndroid app\n\nGenerate a temporary code, then enter it in Android setup.\n\nAdd Android device\nADVANCED TOKEN SETUP\nInstall the AI Memory extension (see extension/README.md for sideload steps).\nOpen chrome://extensions, find AI Memory, click Details → Extension options.\nSet AI Memory URL to https://brain.arunp.in and copy the token from advanced setup into the Token field.\nClick Test connection, then Save.\nShow advanced token setup\n\nChrome does not allow a website to open an extension's options page automatically; chrome:// links must be navigated manually.",
